songs.title: The Interlude That Never Ends (2018)
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
It just keeps me wonderin' this goddamn silence
It just keeps me going insane
Numb the pain like I was on Novocaine
Numb the pain, pain
It just keeps me wonderin' this goddamn silence
It just keeps me going insane
Numb the pain like I was on Novocaine
Numb the pain, pain
